Step and fold, step and flip, step and slide, step and cross fold.

sdr> /// step and slide
sdr> /program = A1
A1
sdr> /setFormation(FormationList.LINES_FACING_OUT)
| 1B^  1G^  2B^  2G^
| 
| 4Gv  4Bv  3Gv  3Bv
