| 
| 1B>  2Gv  1G>  4Bv
sdr> /// These examples from tidal wave require us to preserve the offset
sdr> /setFormation(FormationList.RH_TIDAL_LINE)
| 1B^  1G^  2B^  2G^  4Gv  4Bv  3Gv  3Bv
sdr> step and slide
| 1G^  2B^
| 
| 1B^  2G^  4Gv  3Bv
| 
|           4Bv  3Gv
